title: Detective Conan Movie 08: Time Travel of the Silver Sky
title_japanese: 名探偵コナン 銀翼のタイムトラベル
title_synonyms: Detective Conan Movie 08: Magician of the Silver Sky Recap
Detective Conan Movie 08: Magician of the Silver Sky Special
Meitantei Conan: Ginyoku no Time Travel
synopsis: Professor Agasa has created a computer program that can give you the identity of anyone in the world. He decides to use it on figuring out who Kaitou Kid is. Before he does, the program gives him a history of the Kid, as well as preview clips of the eighth movie. When he is about to finally figure out who the Kid is, Kid appears on the computer screen, announcing he has hacked the program. (Source: detectiveconanworld)
